edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter

Class Environment

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.PropertiesExtender
      • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.Environment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEnvironment, IPropertiesExtender
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractShell

    public class Environment
extends PropertiesExtender
implements IEnvironment, IPropertiesExtender
    Provides thread-safe methods to set and get environment variables. Delegation of environment to another IEnvironment is supported.

      • getDelegateEnvironment

        public IEnvironment getDelegateEnvironment()
        Description copied from interface: IEnvironment
        Get the delegated environment.
        If delegation occurs, the getEnv, setEnv, and getEnvNames methods use only the delegated environment and not this environment. This is unlike Properties, which searches defaultProperties only if local search fails.
        Specified by:
